  <h1>Cron Expression Generator</h1>
  <p><strong>Examples:</strong>
    <button onclick="setExample('0 0 * * *')">Every day at midnight</button>
    <button onclick="setExample('*/5 * * * *')">Every 5 minutes</button>
    <button onclick="setExample('30 9 * * 1')">Mondays at 9:30 AM</button>
  </p>
  <p>Build a cron expression and understand what it actually means.</p>

  <div>
    <label>Minute:</label>
    <select id="min">
      <option value="*">Every minute</option>
      <option value="*/5">Every 5 minutes</option>
      <option value="0">00</option>
      <option value="1">01</option>
      <option value="2">02</option>
      <!-- ... up to 59 -->
      <option value="59">59</option>
    </select>
